00:03:27.510 --> 00:03:30.615
But you get a
little bit of-- you

00:03:30.615 --> 00:03:32.520
know, you get the
creative people.

00:03:32.520 --> 00:03:35.480
There tends to be
relatives of people

00:03:35.480 --> 00:03:37.610
