00:06:02.720 --> 00:06:06.370
Now I like to look at
personality differences

00:06:06.370 --> 00:06:08.950
sort of like a
music mixing board.

00:06:08.950 --> 00:06:10.270
It's not black and white.

00:06:10.270 --> 00:06:14.100
If I get a diagnosis for
tuberculosis, that's definite.

00:06:14.100 --> 00:06:16.420
I either got
tuberculosis or I don't.

00:06:16.420 --> 00:06:19.390
Or I've either had
tuberculosis or I didn't.

00:06:19.390 --> 00:06:21.640
So when I check the
Australian customs form, which

00:06:21.640 --> 00:06:23.940
I did two months
ago, I can check

00:06:23.940 --> 00:06:26.740
