technology, which

00:09:32.500 --> 00:09:36.990
I'm sure some Asperger people
had to develop the computer

00:09:36.990 --> 00:09:39.995
to enable this scanner to
track white matter fibers.

00:09:39.995 --> 00:09:42.520
So your brain's got the
gray matter on the outside.

00:09:42.520 --> 00:09:44.970
And the inside of the
brain is all white matter,

00:09:44.970 --> 00:09:47.460
big long axons that go all
the way across the brain that

00:09:47.460 --> 00:09:49.080
form cable bundles.

00:09:49.080 --> 00:09:50.850
And this new
technology can actually

00:09:50.850 --> 00:09:53.460
dissect out the cable bundles.

00:09:53.460 --> 00:09:55.570
It can tell the difference
between a bridge that

00:09:55.570 --> 00:09:58.030
