the entire class.

00:43:41.700 --> 00:43:43.890
I don't consider that a failure.

00:43:43.890 --> 00:43:45.630
Because there's an
awful lot of people

00:43:45.630 --> 00:43:47.910
that might want to just look
at some programming stuff

00:43:47.910 --> 00:43:50.076
